    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/792f3d21f83516015d3bc87812105217.poster.avif?t=1729318325\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/792f3d21f83516015d3bc87812105217.webm?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/792f3d21f83516015d3bc87812105217.mp4?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage your own medieval tavern</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bartenders is a multiplayer tavern simulation game where you serve customers and build up your reputation. Prepare and serve your best dishes in a physics-based environment. Unlock new recipes and try to prepare the best dish in town. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/66bb10359d733a6cf0f35986a4b92985.poster.avif?t=1729318325\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/66bb10359d733a6cf0f35986a4b92985.webm?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/66bb10359d733a6cf0f35986a4b92985.mp4?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade and advance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy and upgrade furniture, equip better tools, and customize your tavern to your liking. Improve your tavern's decor to attract more customers and start to serve to the upper class. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/d88cd73e9a1d050b77016c4be8b659dc.poster.avif?t=1729318325\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/d88cd73e9a1d050b77016c4be8b659dc.webm?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/d88cd73e9a1d050b77016c4be8b659dc.mp4?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your friends or hire to boost your servicing capacity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 10 friends together, and hire NPCs to share the workload.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/5f2fbf7bdecee7993080fd79c4036c4e.poster.avif?t=1729318325\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/5f2fbf7bdecee7993080fd79c4036c4e.webm?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/5f2fbf7bdecee7993080fd79c4036c4e.mp4?t=1729318325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Day and night cycle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open your tavern at night, interact with the village, and upgrade your tavern during the day.</p>",
